The,WSDOT,Traveler,API,s,provides,a,single,gateway,to,all,of,WSDOT,s,data,The,Washington,State,Ferry,Schedule,data,service,includes,planned,departures,adjustments,contingencies,and,more,The,Washington,State,Department,of,Transportation,is,the,steward,of,a,multimodal,transportation,system,and,responsible,for,ensuring,that,people,and,goods,move,safely,and,efficiently,In,addition,to,building,maintaining,and,operating,the,state,highway,system,WSDOT,is,responsible,for,the,state,ferry,system,and,works,in,partnership,with,others,to,maintain,and,improve,local,roads,railroads,and,airports,as,well,as,to,support,alternatives,to,driving,such,as,public,transportation,bicycles,and,pedestrian,programs